title: Waves v9r13 Crack Only For Windoes
description:
Latest update from Waves

This is the crack only!!!
you will need to download the full exe. installer from Waves.com

You can read the nfo file included in this torrent to see what has changed, but be aware that this does not include any new plug-ins (Waves hasn't released any) or AAX support (yet, Waves is still on porting there plug-ins)


The choice is yours if whether or not you want to download this update or if its of any use to you, if you were having issues with the plug-ins crashing your DAW on a Win 8 system then this may address that issue, minor GUI issues were also fixed

Tested in Pro Tools 10.3.7 and FL Studio 11.0.1 (R2R release)
